\c 33
\s Okuhle kuzabuyiswa eJerusalema
\p
\v 1 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kuJeremiya ngokwesibili, esavalelwe egumeni lentolongo,\x + 32.2; 37.4.\x* lisithi:
\v 2 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, ekwenzayo,\x + Isa. 37.26.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd*, ekubumbayo, ukukumisa;\x + Isa. 37.26.\x* uJehova libizo lakhe:\x + 16.21. Amos 4.13.\x*
\v 3 Ngibiza, ngikuphendule,\x + 29.12. Hlab. 91.15.\x* ngikwazise izinto ezinkulu lezifihlakeleyo elingazaziyo.\x + Isa. 48.6.\x*
\v 4 Ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wakoIsrayeli, ngezindlu zalumuzi langezindlu zamakhosi akoJuda, ezidilizelwe phansi ukuba ngamadundulu langenxa yenkemba:\x + 32.24.\x*
\v 5 Beza ukulwa lamaKhaladiya,\x + 32.5.\x* kodwa bayazigcwalisa ngezidumbu zabantu engibatshayileyo ekuthukutheleni kwami lekufuthekeni kwami,\x + Hez. 22.20.\x* njalo engifihle ubuso bami kulumuzi ngenxa yobubi babo bonke.\x + Dute. 31.17.\x*
\v 6 Khangela, ngizawandisela impilo enhle lokusiliswa;\x + 30.17.\x* ngibelaphe,\x + 30.17.\x* ngibembulele ukwanda kokuthula leqiniso.
\v 7 Ngizabuyisa ukuthunjwa kukaJuda lokuthunjwa kukaIsrayeli,\x + 30.3; 33.11,26.\x* ngibakhe\x + 24.6; 31.4,28.\x* njengakuqala.\x + 30.20; 33.11. Isa. 1.26.\x*
\v 8 Ngibahlambulule kubo bonke ububi babo abona ngabo kimi,\x + Hez. 36.25. Heb. 9.13,14.\x* ngithethelele zonke iziphambeko zabo\x + 31.34.\x* abona ngazo kimi labaphambeka ngazo kimi.
\p
\v 9 Njalo kuzakuba kimi libizo lenjabulo,\x + 13.11.\x* kube ludumo, njalo kube yibuhle, kuzo zonke izizwe zomhlaba ezizakuzwa konke okuhle engibenzela khona; zesabe\x + Isa. 60.5. Hlab. 130.4.\x* zithuthumele ngakho konke okuhle langakho konke ukuthula engibenzela khona.\x + Dute. 2.25.\x*
\v 10 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Kuzabuya kuzwakale kulindawo, elithi ngayo, ilunxiwa, engelamuntu lengelanyamazana,\x + 32.43.\x* emizini yakoJuda\x + 11.6.\x* lezitaladeni zeJerusalema,\x + 11.6.\x* ezilunxiwa okungelamuntu lokungelamhlali lokungelanyamazana,\x + 4.7.\x*
\v 11 ilizwi lokuthaba, lelizwi lentokozo,\x + 7.34.\x* ilizwi lomyeni, lelizwi likamakoti, ilizwi labathi: Dumisani iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ilungile, ngoba isihawu sayo \add simi\add* kuze kube nininini;\x + 1 Lan. 16.34,41. Isa. 12.4.\x* \add ilizwi\add* lalabo abaletha indumiso endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*.\x + 30.19. Levi 7.12. Hlab. 107.22.\x* Ngoba ngizabuyisa ukuthunjwa kwelizwe\x + 30.3; 33.11,26.\x* njengakuqala,\x + 30.20; 33.11. Isa. 1.26.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 12 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla: Kule indawo elunxiwa engelamuntu kuze kube senyamazaneni,\x + Hez. 36.11.\x* lemizini yonke yayo, kuzabuya kube khona imizi yabelusi\x + 31.24; 50.19. Isa. 65.10. Hez. 34.14.\x* abazakwenza imihlambi ilale \add kuyo\add*.\x + Isa. 13.0.\x*
\v 13 Emizini yentabeni,\x + 17.26; 32.44.\x* emizini yesihotsha,\x + 17.26; 32.44.\x* lemizini yeningizimu,\x + 17.26; 32.44.\x* lelizweni lakoBhenjamini,\x + 17.26; 32.44.\x* lemaphandleni eJerusalema,\x + 17.26; 32.44.\x* lemizini yakoJuda,\x + 17.26; 32.44.\x* izimvu zizabuya zedlule\x + Levi 27.32.\x* ngaphansi kwezandla\x + 5.31.\x* zalowo obalayo,\x + Joha. 10.3.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 14 Khangela, insuku ziyeza,\x + 23.5,6; 33.16.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, lapho ngizamisa ilizwi elihle engilikhulume endlini kaIsrayeli lendlini kaJuda.\x + 29.10.\x*
\p
\v 15 Ngalezonsuku langalesosikhathi ngizahlumisela uDavida iHlumela elilungileyo; njalo uzakwenza isahlulelo lokulunga elizweni.
\v 16 Ngalezonsuku uJuda uzasindiswa, leJerusalema ihlale ivikelekile. Njalo yileli \add ibizo\add* elizabizwa ngalo: IN\nd kosi\nd* ukulunga kwethu.
\p
\v 17 Ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Kakuyikuqunywa muntu kuDavida\x + 1 Kho. 2.4. Hlab. 89.4.\x* ohlala esihlalweni sobukhosi sendlu kaIsrayeli.\x + 22.2; 33.21.\x*
\v 18 Njalo kakuyikuqunywa muntu kubapristi, amaLevi, ebusweni bami,\x + 33.21. Isa. 66.21.\x* onikela umnikelo wokutshiswa,\x + 3.16. Roma 12.1; 15.16. Heb. 13.15,16. 1 Pet. 2.5,9. Isam. 1.6; 5.10; 20.6.\x* atshise umnikelo wokudla,\x + 1.16.\x* enze umhlatshelo insuku zonke.
\p
\v 19 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kuJeremiya lisithi:
\v 20 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Uba lingasephula isivumelwano sami semini lesivumelwano sami sobusuku,\x + 31.36; 33.25. Hlab. 72.5. Gen. 8.22.\x* ukuze kungabi khona imini lobusuku ngesikhathi sakho,
\v 21 khona sizakwephulwa isivumelwano sami loDavida inceku yami,\x + Hlab. 89.34.\x* ukuze angabi landodana yokubusa esihlalweni sakhe sobukhosi,\x + 22.2; 33.21.\x* le\add sivumelwano\add* lamaLevi, abapristi, izikhonzi zami.\x + 33.21. Isa. 66.21.\x*
\v 22 Njengoba ibutho lamazulu lingebalwe,\x + Gen. 15.5.\x*\x + 31.37.\x* letshebetshebe lolwandle lingelinganiswe,\x + Gen. 22.17.\x* ngokunjalo ngizakwandisa inzalo kaDavida inceku yami lamaLevi angikhonzayo.
\p
\v 23 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kuJeremiya lisithi:
\v 24 Kawubonanga yini abakutshoyo lababantu besithi: Izinsapho ezimbili iN\nd kosi\nd* ebizikhethile izilahlile\x + 31.37.\x*? Yebo badelela abantu bami, ukuthi bangabe besaba yisizwe phambi kwabo\x + 31.36.\x*.
\v 25 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Uba isivumelwano sami singeyisiso esemini lesebusuku,\x + 31.36; 33.25. Hlab. 72.5. Gen. 8.22.\x* \add uba\add* ngingamisanga\x + Hlab. 74.16,17; 104.19.\x* izimiso zamazulu lezomhlaba,\x + 31.35.\x*
\v 26 khona ngizayala inzalo kaJakobe lekaDavida inceku yami,\x + 31.37.\x* ukuthi kangiyikuthatha enzalweni yakhe \add ukuze\add* abuse phezu kwenzalo kaAbrahama, uIsaka, loJakobe; ngoba ngizabuyisa ukuthunjwa kwabo,\x + 30.3; 33.7,11.\x* ngibe lesihawu kibo.\x + 12.15.\x*